snippet.title: [OFFICIAL] Expeditions: Conquistador Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Expeditions: Conquistador is out on May 30th, 2013 for PC, Mac and Linux.

Preorder Expeditions: Conquistador from one of the following sites:
Desura @ http://www.desura.com/games/expeditions-conquistador
Gamersgate @ http://www.gamersgate.com/DD-EXCONQ/expeditions-conquistador
GOG.com @ http://www.gog.com/gamecard/expeditions_conquistador
Greenman Gaming @ http://www.greenmangaming.com
Steam @ http://store.steampowered.com/app/237430

Follow us on Twitter @ http://www.twitter.com/LogicArtists
Like us on Facebook @ http://www.facebook.com/ExpeditionsConquistador
Visit our website for future updates @ http://www.conquistadorthegame.com
